Why Blind SSRF is Dangerous
The Attack Surface

Even without seeing responses, attackers can:

    Port Scan Internal Networks - Map internal infrastructure

    Identify Running Services - By response patterns/timing

    Trigger Internal Actions - REST APIs, admin functions

    Access Metadata Endpoints - Cloud credentials (MOST CRITICAL)

    Perform Internal Reconnaissance - Hostnames, services

